c: 20
v: 115
t: "wlqd wasayna adam min qabl 'an yakul min alshjrt, 'alaa yakul mnha, waqulna lh: 'iina 'iiblis eaduun lak wlzwjk, fala yukhrijanakuma min aljnt, ftshqa 'ant wazawjuk fi aldnya, fawaswas 'iilayh alshaytan fataeh, wanasi adam alwsyt, walam najid lah quatan fi aleazm yahfaz biha ma 'umr bh"